# containsProtectedContent

**Type Property**

A flag that indicates whether the object contains protected content.

## Declaration

```swift
static let containsProtectedContent: NSAccessibility.Attribute
```

## Discussion

The value is an `NSNumber` as `boolValue`. The value is [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/true] if the object contains protected content, and [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false] if not.
